data.description: Just what you are looking for!  This adorable three bedroom, one bathroom brick ranch in the heart of Rock Hill is an absolute must see!  Lot of updates, large fenced-in backyard and a huge workshop with electricity! Owner has added energy efficient windows, privacy fence, new gutters, new HVAC and re-installed the attic.  Conveniently located near shopping, dining, parks and I-77!  You can't ask for more!
